To meet our customers’ needs and the constantly changing demands of the markets, Siemens draws on a global sales force that takes its guidance from our regional companies. Key success factors include a strong customer focus, digital transformation, efficient processes, and collaboration with external partners.

1 We call any current or potential purchaser of Siemens products or services, no matter what the sales channel, a “customer.” Some customers who are especially significant for Siemens are called “Key Customers”.